---
---
<section id="precios" class="py-20 sm:py-28 bg-slate-50/50 border-t border-b border-dust-grey/40 relative">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 relative z-10">
    <!-- Header -->
    <div class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-16 sm:mb-20">
      <h2 class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-emerald-700 mb-3 font-mono">Planes y Precios</h2>
      <h3 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900 tracking-tight text-balance mb-4">
        Soluciones flexibles y transparentes para tu organización
      </h3>
      <p class="text-base text-slate-600 text-pretty">
        Selecciona el nivel de automatización y soporte legal adecuado para el tamaño de tu plantilla y necesidades de compliance.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Pricing Grid -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 max-w-6xl mx-auto items-stretch">
      
      <!-- Plan 1: Esencial (Canal Interno) -->
      <div class="bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-2xl p-8 flex flex-col justify-between hover:border-emerald-600 hover:shadow-md transition duration-300 relative overflow-hidden group">
        <!-- Top decorative gradient line -->
        <div class="absolute top-0 inset-x-0 h-1.5 bg-slate-200 group-hover:bg-emerald-600 transition-colors"></div>

        <div>
          <div class="mb-6">
            <h4 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2 font-serif-title">Esencial (Canal Interno)</h4>
            <p class="text-xs text-slate-500 leading-relaxed">
              Cumplimiento normativo básico para pequeñas empresas. Canal 100% anónimo con gestión interna independiente.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="mb-6">
            <span class="text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900">$49</span>
            <span class="text-sm text-slate-500 font-medium">USD / mes</span>
          </div>
          
          <ul class="space-y-4 text-xs sm:text-sm text-slate-700 mb-8 border-t border-slate-100 pt-6">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg class="h-4 w-4 text-emerald-600 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
              </svg>
              <span>Canal de denuncias 100% anónimo y seguro</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg class="h-4 w-4 text-emerald-600 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
              </svg>
              <span>Formulario estándar y configurable</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg class="h-4 w-4 text-emerald-600 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
              </svg>
              <span>Enlace web y Código QR para difusión</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg class="h-4 w-4 text-emerald-600 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
              </svg>
              <span>Gestión interna autónoma (1 administrador)</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-slate-400">
              <svg class="h-4 w-4 text-slate-300 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12" />
              </svg>
              <span class="line-through">Sin Inteligencia Artificial (triage manual)</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-slate-400">
              <svg class="h-4 w-4 text-slate-300 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12" />
              </svg>
              <span class="line-through">Gestión e investigación legal delegada</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        
        <a href="#contacto" class="w-full py-3 px-4 text-center text-sm font-semibold text-slate-700 bg-slate-100 hover:bg-slate-200 border border-slate-200 rounded-md transition duration-200 focus:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-emerald-500">
          Iniciar Plan Esencial
        </a>
      </div>

      <!-- Plan 2: Gestor Pro (Híbrido) -->
      <div class="relative bg-white border-2 border-emerald-600 rounded-2xl p-8 flex flex-col justify-between shadow-[0_4px_25px_rgba(4,120,87,0.05)] hover:shadow-[0_4px_30px_rgba(4,120,87,0.12)] transition duration-300">
        <!-- Highlight badge -->
        <div class="absolute -top-3.5 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 px-3.5 py-1 rounded-full bg-emerald-700 text-white text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider">
          Recomendado
        </div>

        <div>
          <div class="mb-6">
            <h4 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2 font-serif-title">Gestor Pro (Híbrido)</h4>
            <p class="text-xs text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
              Plataforma con IA para optimizar la gestión interna, y flexibilidad de derivar casos difíciles a abogados expertos.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="mb-6">
            <span class="text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900">$149</span>
            <span class="text-sm text-slate-500 font-medium">USD / mes</span>
          </div>
          
          <ul class="space-y-4 text-xs sm:text-sm text-slate-700 mb-8 border-t border-slate-100 pt-6">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg class="h-4 w-4 text-emerald-600 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
              </svg>
              <span class="font-medium">Incluye todas las bases del Plan Esencial</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg class="h-4 w-4 text-emerald-600 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
              </svg>
              <span class="font-semibold text-emerald-700">Asistente de IA Activo (triage, resúmenes y alertas)</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg class="h-4 w-4 text-emerald-600 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
              </svg>
              <span>Chat bidireccional anónimo con traducción automática</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg class="h-4 w-4 text-emerald-600 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
              </svg>
              <span class="font-semibold text-emerald-700">Derivación de casos bajo demanda a abogados especialistas</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg class="h-4 w-4 text-emerald-600 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
              </svg>
              <span>Hasta 3 administradores independientes</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg class="h-4 w-4 text-emerald-600 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
              </svg>
              <span>Trazabilidad inmutable sellada digitalmente</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        
        <a href="#contacto" class="w-full py-3.5 px-4 text-center text-sm font-bold text-white bg-emerald-700 hover:bg-emerald-800 rounded-md shadow-sm transition duration-200 focus:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-emerald-500">
          Iniciar Plan Pro
        </a>
      </div>

      <!-- Plan 3: Full Compliance (Delegado) -->
      <div class="bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-2xl p-8 flex flex-col justify-between hover:border-emerald-600 hover:shadow-md transition duration-300 relative overflow-hidden group">
        <!-- Top decorative gradient line -->
        <div class="absolute top-0 inset-x-0 h-1.5 bg-slate-200 group-hover:bg-emerald-600 transition-colors"></div>

        <div>
          <div class="mb-6">
            <h4 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2 font-serif-title">Full Compliance (Delegado)</h4>
            <p class="text-xs text-slate-500 leading-relaxed">
              Externalización total. Recepción, triage e investigación de denuncias lideradas 100% por abogados especialistas.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="mb-6">
            <span class="text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900">Personalizado</span>
            <span class="text-sm text-slate-500 font-medium">/ corporativo</span>
          </div>
          
          <ul class="space-y-4 text-xs sm:text-sm text-slate-700 mb-8 border-t border-slate-100 pt-6">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg class="h-4 w-4 text-emerald-600 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
              </svg>
              <span class="font-medium">Incluye plataforma Pro con IA y chat anónimo</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg class="h-4 w-4 text-emerald-600 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
              </svg>
              <span class="font-semibold text-emerald-700">Operación total externalizada a abogados dedicados</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg class="h-4 w-4 text-emerald-600 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
              </svg>
              <span>Máxima imparcialidad garantizada frente a auditorías</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg class="h-4 w-4 text-emerald-600 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
              </svg>
              <span>Informes consolidados directos para el Directorio</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg class="h-4 w-4 text-emerald-600 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
              </svg>
              <span>Integración con Directorios Activos (SSO) y ERPs</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg class="h-4 w-4 text-emerald-600 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
              </svg>
              <span>Acuerdos de Nivel de Servicio (SLA) y soporte 24/7</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        
        <a href="#contacto" class="w-full py-3 px-4 text-center text-sm font-semibold text-slate-700 bg-slate-100 hover:bg-slate-200 border border-slate-200 rounded-md transition duration-200 focus:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-emerald-500">
          Contactar Ventas
        </a>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>
